[REGION:fullwidth]

![](Reflections_1_6_Header.png)

**Scene Capture Cubes** capture a fully dynamic cube map from their location _on every frame_. This requires a Cubemap Render Target to actually capture to, and then that Render Target can be used as a texture within any Material. 

[REGION:warning]
Scene Capture Cubes are quite expensive in terms of performance and should be used only when they are absolutely required to achieve a given effect.
[/REGION]

